<p>
<strong>The Benefits of a Solid Objective</strong></p>

<p>A 
<a href="http://www.staples.com/Any-Time-Organizer-Deluxe-Version-14-Boxed-CD/product_369334">customer service resume objective</a> is often overlooked by applicants, but an outstanding objective provides many benefits. It helps potential employers understand your expected goals within the company. And helps elevate you above the rest by showing the interviewer that you have goals that are in line with the company's expectation for the position. Including a powerful objective also demonstrates your goal-setting abilities and attentiveness to planning.</p>

